structured_info.description: AFCONS is the flagship infrastructure engineering and construction company of the Shapoorji Pallonji group, a diversified Indian conglomerate, with over six decades of legacy. They have a strong track record of executing numerous complex, challenging and unique EPC projects both within India and internationally. Afcons has projects in over 25 countries in Asia, Africa, and the Middle East. Afcons is ranked 6th globally in Marine and Port facilities, and 21st globally in the Bridges sector*. It is the only Indian company in Top 25 International Contractors in both sectors*. Afcons is also the highest-ranking Indian contractor in Top 50 International Contractors in Transportation sector*. It is a leader in Marine, LNG, and Metro Rail in India. They aim to be a Knowledge Enterprise, focusing on identifying, growing, and deploying Knowledge Assets for accelerated learning, innovation, and better execution.

All_real_estate_projects.name: Udhampur-Srinagar-Baramulla Rail Link Project
All_real_estate_projects.description: One of the most ambitious railway projects of Govt of India, marking a new era of transformation in J&K. Afcons has been instrumental in bringing this project to life, having constructed the world’s highest single-arch railway bridge, India’s longest railway tunnel, and multiple bridges & tunnels on this route.

All_real_estate_projects.name: Chenab Railway Bridge
